data.description: This well-kept manufactured home on a beautiful 2.14 acre tract of property in the highly desired Needville ISD can be yours today! This property boasts a nicely wooded large corner lot location giving you access from both Kincer & Oak Forest Roads. You'll enjoy evenings relaxing on your back deck overlooking your back yard, and your pups will enjoy the outdoors in a large separetly fenced-in pen in the side yard. Inside you'll find a huge living area that opens into the spacious kitchen-dining room combo. This split floorplan allows for the primary bedroom w/ensuite on one side of the home and 2 additional bedrooms and a guest bathroom on the opposite side of the home. You'll appreciate the large utility room that allows for the convenience of an in-home laundry area and a half-bath that's easily accessible by your guests. Dining room table & chairs, washer, dryer, refrigerator, freezer, and extra hot water heater (in shed) convey with sale.
